1
00:00:12,280 --> 00:00:16,160
Under the bridge in front of the door,

2
00:00:16,800 --> 00:00:19,760
swims a flock of ducks.

3
00:00:29,080 --> 00:00:29,720
Officer,

4
00:00:30,160 --> 00:00:31,560
after I finish the discharge procedures,

5
00:00:31,560 --> 00:00:33,040
I can go home, right?

6
00:00:33,480 --> 00:00:33,880
Yeah.

7
00:00:34,160 --> 00:00:35,600
You should stay in Jiangcheng for now.

8
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:38,760
The police still need your cooperation with the investigation.

9
00:00:38,760 --> 00:00:39,520
Okay.

10
00:01:02,480 --> 00:01:03,280
Yang Xiaomei.

11
00:01:06,240 --> 00:01:08,000
The results of your psychiatric evaluation

12
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:10,240
and polygraph test are out.

13
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:12,440
Are you

14
00:01:12,840 --> 00:01:14,700
still planning to keep up the act?

15
00:01:22,680 --> 00:01:23,480
Yang Xiaomei,

16
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:24,940
from Nancheng.

17
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:27,400
You worked at the Nancheng Meat Processing Plant

18
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:28,660
and a garment factory.

19
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:30,880
Your dismemberment skills,

20
00:01:31,360 --> 00:01:33,960
you learned them at the meat plant, didn't you?

21
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:53,180
You don't investigate Wang Xichuan,

22
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:54,539
Wang Mingming,

23
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:56,440
and Yang Zhigang,

24
00:01:58,400 --> 00:02:00,130
but you come to investigate me.

25
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:02,480
We will.

26
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:05,240
We will investigate everything clearly.

27
00:02:05,240 --> 00:02:07,300
The police won't wrong a good person,

28
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:09,220
nor will we let a bad person go.

29
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:13,220
It's been three years.

30
00:02:14,640 --> 00:02:17,400
You haven't found Wang Xi for three years.

31
00:02:23,079 --> 00:02:25,000
How can I trust you?

32
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:29,400
This matter

33
00:02:29,760 --> 00:02:32,890
is indeed a dereliction of duty on the part of the police.

34
00:02:33,079 --> 00:02:34,079
On behalf of them,

35
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:35,300
I apologize to you.

36
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:38,760
I sympathize with your experience,

37
00:02:38,760 --> 00:02:40,420
and I understand your hatred.

38
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,200
But

39
00:02:42,720 --> 00:02:45,120
the price you pay for doing this is too high.

40
00:02:45,760 --> 00:02:46,760
To trade your life

41
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,940
for the life of such an animal,

42
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:50,780
do you think it's worth it?

43
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:56,600
For your case,

44
00:02:56,720 --> 00:02:58,120
as long as you plead guilty,

45
00:02:58,120 --> 00:03:00,580
your sentence can be reduced at discretion.

46
00:03:01,160 --> 00:03:02,560
You are still very young.

47
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:05,000
We hope you can tell the truth

48
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:07,480
and make a clean break with the past.

49
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:09,620
This way you can start your life anew.

50
00:03:18,200 --> 00:03:18,600
Well,

51
00:03:19,920 --> 00:03:22,380
if you don't want to talk, we won't force you.

52
00:03:22,480 --> 00:03:24,010
Whenever you figure it out,

53
00:03:24,079 --> 00:03:25,280
notify us at any time.

54
00:03:26,320 --> 00:03:27,180
Let's go first.

55
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:28,840
Okay.

56
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:29,840
Okay.

57
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:33,720
I'll talk.

58
00:03:39,200 --> 00:03:40,320
Start recording.

59
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:47,040
This...

60
00:03:47,760 --> 00:03:50,400
was found in the dry well near the Wang family's house.

61
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:52,320
It has Wang Xichuan's blood on it,

62
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:54,620
as well as your fingerprints.

63
00:03:56,079 --> 00:03:56,880
Yang Xiaomei.

64
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:59,020
On the day of the incident,

65
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:00,730
what exactly happened?

66
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:06,920
That night,

67
00:04:09,200 --> 00:04:11,060
I stole the key from Wang Mingming

68
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:14,010
and escaped the cellar.

69
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,120
I wanted to run away,

70
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:20,160
but looking like that,

71
00:04:21,279 --> 00:04:22,400
where could I go?

72
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,400
It just so happened that day,

73
00:04:27,400 --> 00:04:29,060
that old bastard Wang Xichuan

74
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,480
was drunk.

75
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:47,159
You killed Wang Xichuan.

76
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,530
He locked me in that cellar,

77
00:04:54,280 --> 00:04:56,200
and tortured me like an animal.

78
00:04:59,880 --> 00:05:03,010
Killing him a hundred times wouldn't satisfy my hatred.

79
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:05,930
How did you dispose of the body?

80
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:09,640
How else could I?

81
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:12,260
Just like slaughtering a pig,

82
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:14,360
I chopped him to pieces.

83
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:36,800
That day,

84
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:40,720
I originally wanted to kill Wang Mingming too.

85
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:43,060
Then I thought,

86
00:05:44,280 --> 00:05:45,680
I might as well frame him.

87
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:48,140
If that failed,

88
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:51,920
I'd let Yang Zhigang take the blame.

89
00:05:53,200 --> 00:05:54,400
If we're going to die,

90
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:55,610
we all die together.

91
00:05:58,880 --> 00:06:00,010
What about the head?

92
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,320
Wang Xichuan's head.

93
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:03,740
Where did you throw it?

94
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:07,600
I don't remember.

95
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:10,020
After finishing that day,

96
00:06:10,760 --> 00:06:11,690
I was dead tired,

97
00:06:12,400 --> 00:06:14,000
so I just threw it somewhere.

98
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:17,740
It probably washed away in the river.

99
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:32,980
When you killed and dismembered him,

100
00:06:33,200 --> 00:06:34,400
where was Lin Xiaoai?

101
00:06:40,840 --> 00:06:41,640
In the cellar.

102
00:06:43,280 --> 00:06:47,000
She was forced to drink charmed water by that old bastard Wang Xichuan

103
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:47,860
and passed out.

104
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,040
Yang Xiaomei.

105
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:55,500
You were imprisoned by them for three years.

106
00:06:55,760 --> 00:06:56,440
Why did you

107
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,980
choose to make your move that day?

108
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:02,880
He ruined me

109
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:05,480
and killed my friend.

110
00:07:06,880 --> 00:07:07,640
That day.

111
00:07:09,440 --> 00:07:10,370
For three years,

112
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:12,400
every day,

113
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:14,520
every moment,

114
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:15,760
I wanted to kill them.

115
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:20,720
Three years ago.

116
00:07:21,520 --> 00:07:22,850
My friend Li Zhaodi and I

117
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,650
were laid off by the factory

118
00:07:25,320 --> 00:07:27,450
and couldn't find new jobs right away.

119
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:29,740
So I dragged her to Wangwu Village

120
00:07:30,080 --> 00:07:31,440
to get our fortunes told by Wang Xichuan.

121
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:31,880
Hey.

122
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:33,280
Zhaodi,

123
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:34,880
look!

124
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:37,930
The scenery here

125
00:07:38,080 --> 00:07:39,010
is so beautiful.

126
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,880
What's so good about it?

127
00:07:40,880 --> 00:07:42,740
My hometown looks just like this.

128
00:07:43,520 --> 00:07:46,280
Do you really believe that Master Wang can change your luck?

129
00:07:46,280 --> 00:07:46,680
Oh,

130
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,170
don't be a buzzkill.

131
00:07:48,200 --> 00:07:50,080
They say he's very accurate.

132
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:52,050
Let's just give it a try.

133
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:53,380
If it doesn't work out,

134
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:55,770
we'll just treat it as a relaxing trip.

135
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:57,320
Ouch.

136
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:58,320
Zhaodi,

137
00:07:58,760 --> 00:08:00,620
thank you for coming here with me.

138
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:13,580
She's dead.

139
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:27,280
The usual.

140
00:08:28,080 --> 00:08:29,440
Go get Yang Zhigang.

141
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:31,610
Have him chop it off.

142
00:08:31,840 --> 00:08:32,640
Throw the body

143
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:35,700
into the green curtain of tall crops and bury it.

144
00:08:36,679 --> 00:08:38,280
That old guy went to the city.

145
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:40,720
The body will stink by the time he gets back.

146
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:41,520
Then you do it.

147
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:49,560
Wang Xichuan,

148
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:51,280
you old bastard.

149
00:08:51,680 --> 00:08:53,240
I am your son.

150
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:56,360
You want me to do such an immoral thing.

151
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:58,000
Are you even a father?

152
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:01,370
If you don't have the guts, just say so.

153
00:09:03,920 --> 00:09:04,520
Forget it.

154
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:06,940
We won't cut off

155
00:09:07,560 --> 00:09:08,620
the head this time.

156
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:11,080
Drag her out

157
00:09:11,160 --> 00:09:13,220
and throw her into the green curtain.

158
00:09:13,880 --> 00:09:15,610
You can at least do that, right?

159
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:25,240
Shoes.

160
00:09:46,920 --> 00:09:47,680
I've said

161
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,850
everything I needed to say.

162
00:09:58,520 --> 00:09:59,640
Stop recording.

163
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:03,080
Thank you.

164
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:16,540
I can't believe it was her.

165
00:10:18,400 --> 00:10:20,120
Even though she was a victim

166
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:23,000
and Wang and his son really deserved to die,

167
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:23,640
but

168
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:25,280
using this method...

169
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:29,520
She's been pretending to be crazy.

170
00:10:30,600 --> 00:10:32,730
Her mental fortitude is quite strong.

171
00:10:32,880 --> 00:10:34,720
With a mental fortitude like hers,

172
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:36,520
she confessed way too smoothly.

173
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:37,640
Don't you think

174
00:10:38,040 --> 00:10:39,440
that's a bit suspicious?

175
00:10:41,800 --> 00:10:42,520
Perhaps

176
00:10:44,800 --> 00:10:46,730
she still wants to hide something.

177
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:49,100
Like the whereabouts of the head.

178
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:53,200
Xiao Zhai.

179
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:55,040
Go check the

180
00:10:55,520 --> 00:10:57,050
missing persons database.

181
00:10:57,480 --> 00:10:58,480
Look up Li Zhaodi.

182
00:10:58,680 --> 00:10:59,160
Okay.

183
00:11:00,680 --> 00:11:01,480
The point is,

184
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:03,640
the two skeletons we found in Qingshazhang

185
00:11:03,640 --> 00:11:04,880
aren't Li Zhaodi's.

186
00:11:06,200 --> 00:11:08,260
There couldn't be a third one, right?

187
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:11,720
Maybe

188
00:11:13,520 --> 00:11:14,720
Li Zhaodi isn't dead.

189
00:11:18,040 --> 00:11:18,970
What do you mean?

190
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,200
Look.

191
00:11:22,400 --> 00:11:23,440
This is the handwriting

192
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:26,900
Li Zhaodi wrote on the fortune-telling paper three years ago.

193
00:11:27,040 --> 00:11:27,700
And this...

194
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:31,760
is Lin Xiaoai's signature on the statement.

195
00:11:31,760 --> 00:11:32,120
Look,

196
00:11:32,880 --> 00:11:34,340
aren't they a bit similar?

197
00:11:41,280 --> 00:11:41,640
Hey.

198
00:11:42,600 --> 00:11:44,200
They do look somewhat alike.

199
00:11:44,400 --> 00:11:45,260
But they are not

200
00:11:45,280 --> 00:11:46,360
exactly the same.

201
00:11:47,920 --> 00:11:49,600
It's possible one was written with the left hand

202
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:51,120
and the other with the right.

203
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:51,380
Hey.

204
00:11:51,560 --> 00:11:53,240
Is Lin Xiaoai left-handed?

205
00:11:55,520 --> 00:11:57,920
When we went to the hospital to question her the other day,

206
00:11:57,920 --> 00:11:58,780
I observed her.

207
00:11:59,400 --> 00:12:00,930
She should be left-handed.

208
00:12:02,920 --> 00:12:03,480
Lin Xiaoai,

209
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:04,740
here's your medicine.

210
00:12:10,920 --> 00:12:12,850
But she used her right hand to sign.

211
00:12:17,160 --> 00:12:18,920
At the time, I thought it was corrected later.

212
00:12:18,920 --> 00:12:20,040
But after seeing Li Zhaodi's handwriting,

213
00:12:20,040 --> 00:12:21,080
I realized

214
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:23,980
she might have done it on purpose.

215
00:12:25,680 --> 00:12:26,480
That does

216
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:28,520
explain the subtle differences between the two handwritings.

217
00:12:28,520 --> 00:12:29,080
So,

218
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:31,440
you suspect Lin Xiaoai

219
00:12:31,960 --> 00:12:33,120
is Li Zhaodi.

220
00:12:33,920 --> 00:12:34,520
Exactly.

221
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:38,080
Hurry and find the handwriting expert

222
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:39,700
to compare and confirm it.

223
00:12:39,880 --> 00:12:40,200
Okay.

224
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:40,800
Oh, right.

225
00:12:41,480 --> 00:12:42,280
Also have them check

226
00:12:42,280 --> 00:12:43,480
the Nushu writing on the cellar wall

227
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:44,520
as well.

228
00:12:44,640 --> 00:12:47,600
The starting angle, turning force, and finishing angle

229
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:48,800
are all very similar.

230
00:12:48,880 --> 00:12:49,840
I suspect

231
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:54,170
she likely had contact with the real mastermind behind the husband's murder.

232
00:12:54,720 --> 00:12:55,450
Understood.

233
00:12:57,880 --> 00:12:58,340
This...

234
00:13:12,840 --> 00:13:15,080
The handwriting and DNA test results

235
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:15,680
are already

236
00:13:15,680 --> 00:13:16,120
out.

237
00:13:20,920 --> 00:13:21,800
That's right.

238
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:23,640
I am Li Zhaodi.

239
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:28,180
Why did you return to Wangwu Village?

240
00:13:29,320 --> 00:13:30,600
To save Yang Xiaomei.

241
00:13:32,680 --> 00:13:34,040
She thought I was dead.

242
00:13:34,520 --> 00:13:35,800
Luckily, I survived.

243
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:37,480
Not only did I stay alive,

244
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:39,410
but I could also go back to save her.

245
00:13:39,920 --> 00:13:41,680
Oh, Zhaodi,

246
00:13:42,040 --> 00:13:43,900
thank you for coming here with me.

247
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:45,920
Instead of seeking someone to change my luck,

248
00:13:45,920 --> 00:13:47,580
I might as well change my name.

249
00:13:49,680 --> 00:13:51,320
I hate the name Zhaodi,

250
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:53,720
but I don't know what to change it to.

251
00:13:54,400 --> 00:13:55,400
Change your name?

252
00:13:57,000 --> 00:13:58,040
Oh, right.

253
00:14:01,600 --> 00:14:02,530
What do you think

254
00:14:02,800 --> 00:14:04,060
about the name Xiao Ai?

255
00:14:13,320 --> 00:14:14,580
If you try to run again,

256
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:16,380
you'll end up like her,

257
00:14:16,680 --> 00:14:17,600
spending the rest of your life

258
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:18,460
locked up here.

259
00:14:30,200 --> 00:14:32,200
Xiaomei, Xiaomei.

260
00:14:32,640 --> 00:14:33,840
Do you still remember me?

261
00:14:33,840 --> 00:14:34,880
I'm Zhaodi.

262
00:14:35,880 --> 00:14:36,840
Look at me.

263
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:41,200
You are Zhaodi.

264
00:14:43,320 --> 00:14:44,850
How did you end up like this?

265
00:14:46,640 --> 00:14:48,120
My name is Lin Xiaoai now.

266
00:14:48,400 --> 00:14:49,640
I had plastic surgery.

267
00:14:49,640 --> 00:14:50,640
Does it look good?

268
00:14:52,920 --> 00:14:54,200
No, no.

269
00:14:54,640 --> 00:14:57,100
You didn't get plastic surgery to look good.

270
00:14:57,680 --> 00:14:58,880
Why did you come back?

271
00:14:59,840 --> 00:15:01,370
Did you come back to save me?

272
00:15:03,600 --> 00:15:04,530
Don't be afraid.

273
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:07,120
I'm here to take you home.

274
00:15:14,280 --> 00:15:17,140
I originally wanted to take her away from that hell.

275
00:15:17,720 --> 00:15:19,560
We already reached the door.

276
00:15:20,120 --> 00:15:23,250
She saw Wang Xichuan slumped over the table, dead drunk.

277
00:15:23,280 --> 00:15:24,680
Suddenly, she didn't want to leave.

278
00:15:24,680 --> 00:15:25,880
She insisted on getting revenge.

279
00:15:25,880 --> 00:15:27,010
I couldn't stop her.

280
00:15:28,520 --> 00:15:29,920
But I can understand her.

281
00:15:30,600 --> 00:15:32,480
After all, they locked her up for three years

282
00:15:32,480 --> 00:15:34,340
and tortured her for three years.

283
00:15:34,640 --> 00:15:36,640
She must hate him even more than I do.

284
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:38,040
So you

285
00:15:38,680 --> 00:15:41,410
saw Yang Xiaomei kill someone with your own eyes?

286
00:15:42,320 --> 00:15:42,960
Yes.

287
00:15:43,920 --> 00:15:46,250
She said she hated Wang Xichuan to the bone

288
00:15:46,320 --> 00:15:49,180
and had to cut him into pieces to satisfy her hatred.

289
00:15:49,800 --> 00:15:51,440
She also wanted to kill Wang Mingming.

290
00:15:51,440 --> 00:15:53,570
I finally managed to talk her out of it.

291
00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:57,200
Then where was Wang Xichuan's head

292
00:15:57,200 --> 00:15:57,920
thrown?

293
00:15:59,480 --> 00:16:00,240
I don't know.

294
00:16:01,400 --> 00:16:02,060
About this,

295
00:16:02,280 --> 00:16:03,880
you should ask Yang Xiaomei.

296
00:16:04,120 --> 00:16:05,320
So you mean

297
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:07,760
Yang Xiaomei did everything?

298
00:16:10,480 --> 00:16:12,000
I helped her a little.

299
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:14,580
She wanted to frame Yang Zhigang.

300
00:16:14,680 --> 00:16:16,680
I had no choice but to turn myself in.

301
00:16:20,240 --> 00:16:22,520
The reason why a killer dismembers a body

302
00:16:23,040 --> 00:16:24,680
is either to vent their emotions

303
00:16:24,680 --> 00:16:25,960
or to

304
00:16:26,760 --> 00:16:27,820
cover up the truth.

305
00:16:29,680 --> 00:16:30,400
Hey, Chen.

306
00:16:31,080 --> 00:16:32,320
I actually think

307
00:16:32,680 --> 00:16:33,640
this case

308
00:16:33,640 --> 00:16:34,720
is more like

309
00:16:35,120 --> 00:16:37,680
Yang Xiaomei and Lin Xiaoai teaming up for revenge,

310
00:16:37,680 --> 00:16:39,040
while Yang Xiaomei

311
00:16:40,080 --> 00:16:41,210
takes all the blame.

312
00:16:41,480 --> 00:16:42,480
I actually think

313
00:16:42,920 --> 00:16:44,400
Lin Xiaoai is lying.

314
00:16:46,120 --> 00:16:47,400
In her narrative,

315
00:16:47,960 --> 00:16:49,640
she keeps shirking her responsibility

316
00:16:49,640 --> 00:16:51,040
and glorifying herself.

317
00:16:51,320 --> 00:16:53,650
If she really wanted to save Yang Xiaomei,

318
00:16:53,680 --> 00:16:55,480
she could have called the police three years ago.

319
00:16:55,480 --> 00:16:57,080
Why did she wait until now to come back?

320
00:16:57,080 --> 00:16:59,800
She probably thought Yang Xiaomei was tortured to death.

321
00:16:59,800 --> 00:17:02,320
Then she only has one purpose in returning to Wangwu Village.

322
00:17:02,320 --> 00:17:02,880
Revenge.

323
00:17:05,720 --> 00:17:07,319
She kept emphasizing

324
00:17:07,319 --> 00:17:10,720
that Yang Xiaomei hates Wang Xichuan and his son more than she does.

325
00:17:10,720 --> 00:17:11,520
In fact,

326
00:17:11,960 --> 00:17:14,119
she did it to hide her own hatred.

327
00:17:14,720 --> 00:17:15,920
More importantly,

328
00:17:16,319 --> 00:17:18,319
they deliberately hid the truth

329
00:17:18,720 --> 00:17:19,440
and refused to tell us

330
00:17:19,440 --> 00:17:21,569
where Wang Xichuan's head was hidden.

331
00:17:22,800 --> 00:17:23,480
Yes.

332
00:17:23,760 --> 00:17:26,240
Wang Xichuan's head hasn't been found yet.

333
00:17:27,319 --> 00:17:28,800
Where could it be hidden?

334
00:17:28,920 --> 00:17:31,320
Wangwu Village, Qingshazhang, the slaughterhouse,

335
00:17:31,320 --> 00:17:32,520
and other nearby places,

336
00:17:32,520 --> 00:17:33,980
we have searched them all.

337
00:17:34,440 --> 00:17:35,400
Could it be

338
00:17:36,320 --> 00:17:39,320
hidden somewhere else along the way?

339
00:17:41,800 --> 00:17:42,520
Zhai.

340
00:17:44,120 --> 00:17:45,640
If you were the killer,

341
00:17:46,480 --> 00:17:48,640
would you leave the head in a fixed place

342
00:17:48,640 --> 00:17:50,370
waiting for someone to find it,

343
00:17:50,720 --> 00:17:52,400
or would you secretly

344
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:54,600
move it to a further place?

345
00:17:55,320 --> 00:17:56,080
Transfer?

346
00:17:57,920 --> 00:17:58,720
How?

347
00:18:00,320 --> 00:18:01,720
Yang Zhigang said

348
00:18:01,720 --> 00:18:04,000
he met Lin Xiaoai at the slaughterhouse.

349
00:18:04,040 --> 00:18:05,960
Lin Xiaoai also said she was there,

350
00:18:05,960 --> 00:18:07,240
walking right into a trap.

351
00:18:07,240 --> 00:18:09,320
Then Lin Xiaoai had plenty of time

352
00:18:09,320 --> 00:18:11,120
to sneak the head into the transport truck

353
00:18:11,120 --> 00:18:12,250
and transfer it out.

354
00:18:12,320 --> 00:18:14,650
And then come out to wait for Yang Zhigang.

355
00:18:22,880 --> 00:18:24,160
This is a slaughterhouse truck.

356
00:18:24,160 --> 00:18:26,000
It leaves at the same time and place every day.

357
00:18:26,000 --> 00:18:27,240
Check the destination of this truck.

358
00:18:27,240 --> 00:18:28,040
I understand.

359
00:18:29,200 --> 00:18:30,400
Could the head be hidden in this truck?
